		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Did what with the DS Lite? Citation?<br /><br />Game Boy Advance: 240x160 pixels<br />Nintendo DS Lite: 256x192 pixels<br /><br />You'd need some sort of circuit to insert the black windowbox pixels at the top, bottom, left, and right.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

